{"tid":2375827,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反黑警涉勾結黑幫案開庭第六天 仍就是否披露臥底警資料爭拗 案件需押後一個月","createTime":"2021-01-22T10:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:22:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0316831139059c22365b97b51a4768525433d915","tid":2375827,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"左起：趙廣林、賴福康、傅裕文及張子健<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jRqt6TPXDN4NjSk0W2uQ36si2QY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MKRCOKCL4NDO3AHH2XGHJROS7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjRqt6TPXDN4NjSk0W2uQ36si2QY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMKRCOKCL4NDO3AHH2XGHJROS7M.jpg&h=302e34a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣反黑組四名警員疑串謀黑幫策劃「假掃蕩」，遭滲入黑幫的O記卧底踢爆，被控串謀妨礙司法公正罪。案件已開庭第六天，控辯雙方仍未就披露臥底警的開銷紀錄和電話通訊等資料達成共識，尚未傳召證人。控方今向法庭申請押後一個月，以待處理披露事宜，案件勢必另再排期。法官下令辯方在押後期間定期匯報工作進度，並明言若任何一方不合作或做法不合理，法庭將傳召他們出庭解釋。<br />\n<br />\n案件今早在區域法院續審，四名警員包括趙廣林、賴福康、傅裕文、張子健（年齡介乎28至54歲）被控於2018年5月2日至7月10日期間，串謀賭場負責人陳少寶、和勝和其中一個派系「阿頂」綽號「菜仔」的王偉軍，以及一名叫「Eddy」的人士犯案。陳少寶早前認罪。<br />\n<br />\n法官勞潔儀早前裁定，控方須披露涉案卧底警員19146自2017年9月29日起的出入境記錄及開支單據。控方今指，雙方需要更多時間商討，「盡量希望可以配合幾多、披露幾多」，若辯方仍不滿意，將正式向法庭提出基於「公眾利益」而豁免披露。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/KPHG6J2AUNA2HBQVQMD7P6RASU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FKPHG6J2AUNA2HBQVQMD7P6RASU%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=89e6b9a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FKPHG6J2AUNA2HBQVQMD7P6RASU%2F&h=a934acb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/KPHG6J2AUNA2HBQVQMD7P6RASU/</a>"},{"pid":"340bd80f3ff37bc6d4442e23a59440aa0a53cbcf","tid":2375827,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491e45c28fd6d6650c6bf384f9ae4778fa936cf1","tid":2375827,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"diu啦，搞咁大場龍鳳都係想個官鬆手D姐<br />\n直接D講咪算"},{"pid":"76cf7f87d9c3d93b9b780d8fcc493be200ba1ee6","tid":2375827,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"搞咁耐一陣又疑點利益歸被告放生"},{"pid":"29d19c92311db50f48138766f9e3c83b9ec3d98e","tid":2375827,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954b265a208c89eaf668ea266809e80c22f81168","tid":2375827,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e5d142d9eca4b24459c39f5fc4363a1f24a9cd","tid":2375827,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}